The paper proposes a joint multi-task learning algorithm for predicting attributes in images using deep convolutional neural networks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of machine learning techniques such as multi-task learning and natural grouping of attributes, which are commonly used in sub-categories such as machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), multimedia (cs.MM), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
